text: Dalia Grau Quintero (born 1 February 1995) is a Cuban water polo player. She was a member of the Cuba women's national water polo team at the 2019 Pan American Games and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites== * dalia-grau-quintero, swimswam Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban water polo players
